name: Urbanites at a Crossroads
description:
We may have walked together, or met side by side at an intersection at one time. But we never greet each other. In the midst of the crowd we often feel lonely and alienated. That's the urbanites.

Size 79 x 109 cm, Produced May 2 2015, Dimensions 5952 x 4169
